303211608/http://comicbookdb.com/title.php?ID=86 |title=Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon at the Comic Book DB}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.diamondcomics.com/Home/1/1/3/123?articleID=8883 |title=Buy One Crouching Tiger Hidden Dragon Volume 5 GN, Get Green Destiny Letter Opener Free!\t|website=[[Diamond Comic Distributors]] }}</ref>\n==Filmography==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|+ List of screenwriting and directing in film\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Credit\n|-\n| 1991\n| [[Robotrix]]\n| Writer, 2nd assistant director\n|-\n| 1992\n| [[Gigolo and Whore II]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=7593&display_set=eng |title=Gigolo and Whore II (1992) at the HKMDB}}</ref>\n| Writer, 1st assistant director\n|-\n| 1992\n| [[Girls Without Tomorrow 1992]]\n| Writer, 1st assistant director\n|-\n| 1993\n| [[First Shot (1993 film)|First Shot]]\n| Writer\n|-\n| 1993\n| [[Spirit of Love (film)|Spirit of Love]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=7750&display_set=eng |title=The Spirit of Love (1993) at the HKMDB}}</ref>\n| Writer\n|-\n| 1993\n| [[3 Days of a Blind Girl]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=7687&display_set=eng |title=3 Days of a Blind Girl (1993) at the HKMDB}}</ref>\n| Writer\n|-\n| 1995\n| [[The Blade (film)|The Blade]]\n| Writer\n|-\n| 1995\n| [[01:00 A.M.]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=8027&display_set=eng |title=01:00 A.M. (1995) at the HKMDB}}</ref>\n| Writer\n|-\n| 1995\n| [[Green Hat (film)|Green Hat]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=8034&display_set=eng |title=Green Hat (1995) at the HKMDB}}</ref>\n| Executive director ([[:zh:\u57f7\u884c\u5c0e\u6f14|\u57f7\u884c\u5c0e\u6f14]])\n|-\n| 1997\n| [[Once Upon a Time in China and America]]\n| Writer\n|-\n| 1998\n| [[The Group (1998 film)|The Group]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hkmdb.com/db